OL,3,CWhat is Badenochism?
OL,5,FAt the heart of the Tory conference
OL,6,Fexhibition is a mocked-up funfair
OL,7,Fstall called "whack-a-taxpayer." It's
OL,8,Fa bit of joshing at Labour's expense,
OL,9,Fbut it is also the intellectual heart
OL,10,Fof Kemi Badenoch's project to revive
OL,11,Fher ailing party.
OL,13,FShe and her Shadow Chancellor, Mel
OL,14,FStride, believe that at some point in
OL,15,Fthe next three and a half years,
OL,16,FBritish voters will suddenly panic
OL,17,Fthat the budget sums of Reform and
OL,18,FLabour don't add up and will surge
OL,19,Fback to the party of Thatcher.
