OL,3,CWhat is Badenochism?
OL,5,FIt is why Mel Stride is today pledging
OL,6,Fspending cuts that he says will save
OL,7,F#47 billion by taking away disability
OL,8,Fpayments from young people with mental
OL,9,Fhealth problems, cutting civil service
OL,10,Fnumbers by more than 120,000,
OL,11,Fwithdrawing entitlement to benefits
OL,12,Fand universal credit from foreign
OL,13,Fnationals, reducing social-housing
OL,14,Fexpenditure and cutting overseas aid
OL,15,Fby 66%.
