OL,3,CWhat is Badenochism?
OL,5,FTheirs is a Thatcherite message to the
OL,6,FBritish people: that it's time to take
OL,7,Ftheir medicine. It's a stark contrast
OL,8,Fto Farage's populist and popular
OL,9,Fpromises of massive unfunded tax cuts
OL,10,Fand Labour's public spending and
OL,11,Finvestment that is relatively generous
OL,12,F(obviously, if you work in a school or
OL,13,Fhospital, you don't feel there's money
OL,14,Fto burn - but these things are
OL,15,Frelative).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
