OL,3,CWhat is Badenochism?
OL,5,FProbably not yet. And maybe not soon
OL,6,Fenough to rescue her from oblivion.
OL,8,FBut Badenoch is almost certainly
OL,9,Fcorrect that if her party cannot stand
OL,10,Ffirm on this fiscal ground, it has no
OL,11,Ffuture at all. And the mood of the
OL,12,Fmany delegates here to whom I have
OL,13,Fspoken is grim determination to hold
OL,14,Ffast to at least this one principle of
OL,15,FThatcherite Toryism.
