OL,3,CWhat is Badenochism?
OL,5,FSo much else of what at least some
OL,6,FTories thought the party stood for -
OL,7,Finternationalism, for example - is
OL,8,Fbeing eviscerated, not least with
OL,9,FBadenoch's commitment to withdraw from
OL,10,Fthe European Convention on Human
OL,11,FRights, abandon statutory targets to
OL,12,Freduce greenhouse gas emissions and
OL,13,Festablish a large new immigration
OL,14,Fpolice service to round up and deport
OL,15,Fmigrants with no permission to be here.
OL,17,FThose on the left of her party may
OL,18,Fwell therefore jump to the Lib Dems.
OL,19,FThere is a risk, therefore, that we
OL,20,Fhaven't yet seen peak Tory shrinkage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
