OL,3,CWhat is Badenochism?
OL,5,FHowever, Badenoch and Stride hope
OL,6,Fthat, in offering a version of
OL,7,FReform's anchor policies, namely its
OL,8,Fassault on immigration, but seemingly
OL,9,Fpresented as more "thought-through"
OL,10,Fand coupled with what they present as
OL,11,Feconomic common sense, some of those
OL,12,Fwho deserted to Reform will return to
OL,13,Fthe fold.
OL,15,FWhether those supposedly misguided
OL,16,FFaragists will see the light before
OL,17,FMay's elections is, however, doubtful.
